## Usage 

The approach can be used in our package as follows:

::: {.cell execution_count=3}
``` {.julia .cell-code}
generator = GravitationalGenerator()
ce = generate_counterfactual(x, target, counterfactual_data, M, generator)
plot(ce)
```

